layed in the closing stages.\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4582, \"end\": 4594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.745582448675855, \"rank\": 0.3412305959367186, \"text\": \"Yorkshireman\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4621}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing stages\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Alistair was one of the people with one lap to go who said to me, 'Anything can happen, mate'.\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alistair\", \"from\": 4684, \"to\": 4692}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4714}, {\"ngram\": \"one lap\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4727}, {\"ngram\": \"Anything\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He shouted that out.\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a pretty special moment to look back at that now.\\\"\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pretty special moment\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The triathlete will now turn his attention to trying to defend his mixed relay title on Monday.\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The triathlete\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"his attention\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4899}, {\"ngram\": \"his mixed relay title\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4941}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confir